01:21:52.480 --> 01:21:54.470
It's not gross.

01:21:55.000 --> 01:21:56.911
Oh, God.

01:21:57.280 --> 01:21:58.380
You wash, I'll dry.

01:21:58.480 --> 01:21:59.660
Yeah.

01:21:59.760 --> 01:22:01.340
